cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.AI, cs.CL 

The paper proposes a new neural network module for high-level tasks on point clouds, which is suitable for classification and segmentation. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper deals with geometric representations and graph convolutional networks, which are relevant to the graphics (cs.GR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper also involves natural language processing (cs.CL) in terms of evaluating and analyzing the proposed approach.
